channel.title: PI Webclient Error Manual
channel.description:
Hello all,
here are a collection of common errors you get while creating a webclient. Many times people will not add something correctly or will forget to do a step. Therefore, I am creating this to assist in the prevention of so many errors that will need answering.
-Love
[hr]
Error 1:(Error from 3lou 55)
[code]Then it finishes loading, but everything is ok like animations,models,sprites and that when u login using lvl 3 its okay, since u login your old account you get a black screen and in console it shows:
Java.lang.nullpointerexecption Java.lang.nullpointerexecption Java.lang.nullpointerexecption[/code] [b][u] This is caused by not having the correct paths to your cache folder.[/u][/b]
I would suggest looking at your modeldecompressor, class36, sprites, and client.java to insure all paths are correct.
[hr]
Error 2: (Error by david4444)
[code]it works fine if I disable model preloading but if I enable the client doesnt load[/code]
[b][u]This is caused by you not having the Raw folder in your cache.[/u][/b]
I would suggest adding the Raw folder to your cache and reuploading the folder contents, not the whole folder itself.
[hr]
Error 3: (Error by yours truly, me;p)
[img]http://i34.tinypic.com/24ay4xl.png[/img]
[b][u]The problem is one of your paths has not been set.[/u][/b]
In my case the issue was I did not set the path to the Raw folder which is in Client.java.
[hr]
Error 4( Error by mastazak)
[code]ava.net.SocketException: Network is unreachable: connect[/code]
[u][b]The problem here is that your Cache link is not valid.[/b][/u]
Reupload your cache to dropbox or fileden
[hr]
Error 5: (Error by ChrissyDee)
[code]load: class client.class not found.[/code]
[b][u]You did not add client as the class that is being manifested. [/u][/b]
Follow my guide [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,490803.0.html]here[/url].
[hr]
Error 6: (Error by Tylers Pur3)
[code]Java\client.java:8243: cannot find symbol symbol : class CacheDownloader location: class client new CacheDownloader(this).downloadCache(); ^ Note: Some input files use unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details. 1 error Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
[b][u]you did not add the Cachedownloader.class[/u][/b]
[hr]
Error 7:(Error by TsGH Mike)
[code]java.lang.ClassFormatError: Incompatible magic value 1008813135 in class file client[/code]
[b][u]it is very likely that you added your cache to the jar file.[/u][/b]
I would suggest removing the cache and adding it to your local disk c or wherever you have targeted it to appear at.
[hr]
Error 8: (Error by Coder Alex)
[code]unzipping2 Sprites/Lunar/LUNARON 26.PNG unzipping2 Sprites/Lunar/LUNARON 27.PNG unzipping2 Sprites/Lunar/LUNARON 28.PNG unzipping2 Sprites/Lunar/LUNARON 29.PNG unzipping2 Sprites/Lunar/LUNARON 3.PNG unzipping2 Sprites/Lunar/LUNARON 30.PNG unzipping2 Sprites/PrayerTab/Thumbs.db java.lang.IllegalArgumentException[/code]
[b]This means it is not unzipping something correctly. [/b]
Make sure you have added all information correctly from the tutorial.
[hr]
Credits:
Error 9:(Error by Jamieday)
[code]java.net.MalformedURLException: unknown protocol: c at java.net.URL.<init>(Unknown Source) at java.net.URL.<init>(Unknown Source) at sun.plugin.util.GrayBoxPainter.setProgressFilter(Unknown Source) at sun.plugin2.applet.Plugin2Manager.setupGrayBoxPainter(Unknown Source) at sun.plugin2.applet.Plugin2Manager.access$700(Unknown Source) at sun.plugin2.applet.Plugin2Manager$AppletExecutionRunnable.run(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Thread.run(Unknown Source) exception: name. java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: name at sun.plugin2.applet.Applet2ClassLoader.addJar(Unknown Source) at sun.plugin2.applet.Applet2Manager.loadJarFiles(Unknown Source) at sun.plugin2.applet.Plugin2Manager$AppletExecutionRunnable.run(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Thread.run(Unknown Source) Exception: java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: name[/code]
Solution:
Make sure you have added the proper cache link, also, do NOT use www in the link.
an example: [code] private String cacheLink = "http://dl.dropbox.com/u/27893202/evoscape.zip"; // Link to cache[/code]
